quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  21,83,"NoJobe khumbula ngenkathi ememeza iNkosi yakhe (ethi), “ngempela ngithintwe inhlupheko futhi wena ungonomusa ukubedlula bonke abanomusa”"
  21,84,Ngakho-ke samphendula sakususa lokho okwakukuyena okuyinhlupheko futhi samnikeza umndeni wakhe kanye nabanjengabo kanye nabo umusa ovela kuthina nesikhumbuzo sezikhonzi (zikaMvelinqangi)
  21,85,No-Ishmayeli no-Idris noDhul Kifl (Isaiah) bonke babengababekezelayo
  21,86,"Futhisabangenisaemseniwethu, ngempelabonababengabanye babalungileyo"
  21,87,"Futhi uDhuh-Nun (uJonah) khumbula ngenkathi ehamba ethukuthele ngakho-ke wacabanga ukuthi angeke simjezise ngakho-ke wamemeza ebumnyameni wathi “akekho omunye uNkulunkulu ngaphandle kwakho, udumo malube kuwe! Ngempela mina bengingomunye wezoni”"
  21,88,"Ngakho-ke samphendula futhi samsindisa enhluphekweni, futhi sibasindisa kanjalo abakholwayo"
  21,89,NoZakariya khumbula ngenkathi ememeza iNkosi yakhe (ethi) “Nkosi yami! Ungangishiyi ngedwa (ngingenayo ingane) kanti wena ungongcono kunazozonke izindlalifa”
  21,90,"Ngakho-ke sawuphendula (umthandazo wakhe) futhi samupha uJohane futhi samenza unkosikazi wakhe wabangolungileyo kuye, ngempela bona babencintisana ekwenzeni izenzo ezilungileyo futhi basibiza (bathandaza) ngothando nangokwesaba futhi babezithobile ngaphambi kwethu"
  21,91,"Futhi lowo owesifazane (uMariya) aqaphela ubumsulwa bakhe, ngakho-ke siphefumulela kuyena ngomoya wethu futhi samenza yena kanye nendodana yakhe (uJesu) uphawu lwemihlaba"
  21,92,Ngempela lena yindlela yenu inkolo eyodwa futhi mina ngiyiNkosi yenu ngakho-ke ngikhonzeni
  21,93,"Futhi balehlukanisa phakathi kwabo udaba lwabo, bonke bayophindela kuthina"
  21,94,Ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani owenza izenzo (ezinhle) ezilungileyo futhi kulapho eyikholwa ngakho-ke angeke yenqatshwe imizamo yakhe futhi ngempela singabalobi bakhe
  21,95,Futhi akuvumelekile edolobheni esalibhubhisa ukuthi bona bangaphindela
  21,96,Kuze kube bayavulelwa uGog noMagog futhi bona bayoqhamuka kuwona wonke amacala behla
  21,97,"Futhi ngempela sesisondele isethembiso (usuku lokwahlulela), lapho amehlo alabo abangakholwanga ayobe egqolozele (bese bethi), “Oh! usizi kuthina sasingakunakile lokhu kepha sasiyizoni”"
  21,98,"Ngempela nina kanye nalokho enikukhonzayo esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi niyoba yizinkuni zokuvuthisa isihogo, nina niyongena kusona"
  21,99,Ukube laba babengonkulunkulu babengeke bangene kusona (isihogo) futhi bonke bayohlala khona ingunaphakade
  21,100,Okwabo lapho phakathi kuyoba ukuquma futhi bona lapho phakathi bayobe bengezwa
  21,101,Ngempela labo abathenjiswa ubuhle obuvela kuthina bayobekwa kude naso
  21,102,"Angeke bazwe ngisho nomncane umsindo waso, futhi bona bayohlala ingunaphakade kulokho imiphefumulo yabo ekufisayo"
  21,103,Alubaphathi kabi uvalo olukhulu kakhulu futhi ziyohlangana nabo izingelosi (ziyothi) “Lolu usuku lwenu okuyilona enanithenjiswe lona.”
  21,104,Ngosuku lapho siyobe sigoqa amazulu kuyobe kunjengokugoqwa kwamaqeqeba emibhalo njengoba sayisungula indalo yokuqala siyoyiveza kabusha (lesi) isethembiso kuthina ngempela siyokwenza (lokhu)
  21,105,Futhi ngempela sabhala kwiZabur emva kwesikhumbuzo ukuthi umhlaba uyodliwa izinceku zami ezilungileyo
  21,106,Ngempela kulokhu kunomyalezo ebantwini abayizikhonzi
  21,107,Futhi asizange sikuthumele ngaphandle kokuba ube ngumusa emihlabeni
  21,108,"Ithi, “kuphela kwembuliwe kumina ukuthi uNkulunkulu wenu nguNkulunkulu oyedwa, ngakube nina nizoba ngabazinikeleyo ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi na?”"
  21,109,"Kephaumabefulathelaithi,“nginibizilenonkengokulinganayo angazi noma kuseduzane noma kukude lokho enethenjiswa kona.”"
  21,110,Ngempela yena uyayazi inkulumo esobala futhi uyakwazi konke lokho enikufihlayo
  21,111,Futhi angazi ukuthi kuyisilingo kunina nenjabulo yesikhashana
  21,112,"Wathi, “Nkosi yami yehlulela ngeqiniso futhi iNkosi yethu ingenomusa ekuyiyona usizo lwayo olubhekana nalokho enikuchazayo”"